Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是卻好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者 我來告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教給你們的戰鬥方式的名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是消耗戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是忍受疼痛而戰的戰術！
