Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對消失的恐懼！祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的攻擊出現了停頓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類陸續突破防線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前進！別放過這個機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡量前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要像這樣 成為這個島就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要擁抱你們大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像媽媽那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 我要和這個島融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們回歸虛無！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:05:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝生存吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 現在存在於此的喜悅 祝福者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是C點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見 用鎖刃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是用於讓人類和祝福者共存的…資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太多了吧 要溢出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大部分都正在往某個地方發送
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北極方面傳來了資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alvis所有伺服器及烏爾德之泉自動接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太龐大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠遠超過了以前接收到的資料量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎他們接觸到了紅音的意志 接觸到了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路線暢通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有系統一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標周邊的情報被自動重新輸入了導航系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁紅音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去鼓勵絕望的我們要活下去的人
