Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決不會讓你們進去
