Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在的吧 你在這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為同化的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體的同化現象復發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要接受治療 一定能康復
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回島上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mir行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在！開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面出現敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的同化開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的Mir想和天空連接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和從大氣層外進攻的祝福者一起覆蓋整個地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化Mk.Ⅶ的武器向他射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見你來扣扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Sein的能量以最大功率發射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則一騎的身體會撐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對牠們而言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或許是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個Mir也和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了證明生與死 存在與虛無是二者一體循環往復的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會誕生於這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到另一個Mir那裡去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在紛紛墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認法芙娜部隊全員平安！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 他們成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下…起風了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內核和島融為了一體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是風…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Nicht？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mir以自己的死給予了祝福者作為個體的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去大家都會被牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來 遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！一騎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點 同步並沒有中斷！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要缺了一個人 同步就會喪失機能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你在戰鬥前告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在與虛無正在交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是將一切歸於虛無的祝福者式的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在現實世界中 我們多半已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們 還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的太空艦隊和大氣層內的祝福者的內核
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們都在燃燒和下墜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發動之前就整艦被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎還完好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和機體的構造同化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把控制權移交給系統
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離陸之後我來操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛得起來嗎 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mir理解了生命的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乙姬…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是她本人再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是對原型的複製
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是偏離了生命本質的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是乙姬的個體轉生成了新的生命…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 她一定會作為內核長大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日來與我們對話的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們以這個島為希望 一直存在於此地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要繼續前進 就能回到島上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了最後關頭 還是被你搭救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教給了祝福者疼痛和存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也了解了他們的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了存在與虛無的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在與…虛無的循環？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經幾乎都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回 回到島上去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起接受治療吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這麼做吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再過不久就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你說什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說 總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去一趟祝福者的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再次創造出自己的實體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道要花多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至有朝一日再度重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅶ應急檢修完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可以出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的精神狀態也很穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7龍穴 開門！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 Mk.Ⅶ 出擊！
