Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡 等著你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:21:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我領悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便生存充滿痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會選擇存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與你再度相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 我一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到你所在的地方
